description: SURVIVAL THE NAME OF THE GAME: ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ Alright, you think that this is easy. Think again. This is a very hard level (ONLY ONE ROOM) but is fun. You start of with all of the weapons to pick up (EXCEPT FOR THE CHAINGUN AND THE CHAINSAW) but if you shoot, you might be killed in a second (MAYBE NOT) but there is limited stuff to pick up so be careful.
